The Report and Replace Cards service process allows customers to report stolen cards, block cards, and start a replacement card request.
Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled
Use the Service Process Studio to enable the Report and Replace Cards service process.
Your agents can capture and submit a customer request to report stolen cards through the Report and Replace Cards OmniScript. A case is then created in Salesforce.
title: Report and Replace Cards Service Process in Financial Services Cloud
